    You (borrower) promises to pay the amount that you are owing the lender and vows to pay the amount within the specified time.
    2. RESPONSIBILITY

    Although this agreement must be signed below by more than one person, borrower understands that we are each as individuals responsible for paying back the full amount.

    3. LATE CHARGE

